/duties-allah-selves-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":22894,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Duties: Rights of Allah, your family, and yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, made a fellowship between Salman and Abu Darda. Salman visited Abu Darda and found his wife Umm Darda dressed in worn-out clothing. He asked her why she was like this. She said, \u201cYour brother Abu Darda is not interested\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/09\/abu-darda-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":22894,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Bid\u2019ah: Anger at seeing innovations in the religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, entered upon me while he was furious. I said, \u201cWhy are you angry?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cBy Allah, I do not recognize any of the affairs of Muhammad among them except that they pray in congregation.\u201d Source: al-Bida' li-Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37895,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/18\/abu-darda-tafakkur\/","url_meta":{"origin":22894,"position":4},"title":"Umm Darda on Tafakkur: Abu Darda\u2019s habit of contemplation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Awn ibn Abdullah reported: I said to Umm Darda, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhat act of worship did Abu Darda perform most often?\u201d Umm Darda said, \u201cReflection and consideration.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 286 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0623\u064f\u0645\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0639\u0650\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25789,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/abu-darda-on-marriage-husband-and-wife-should-try-to-please-each-other\/","url_meta":{"origin":22894,"position":5},"title":"Abu Darda on Marriage: Husband and wife should try to please each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn Adham reported: Abu Darda said to his wife Umm Darda, may Allah be pleased with both of them, \u201cIf I become angry, then try to please me. If you become angry, then I will try to please you. Were we not to act this way, how quickly would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/da